<%- include("partials/head") %>
<%- include("partials/nav") %>

<main class="shell page-grid reveal">
  <section class="content-flow">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h2>This page keeps the feedback function from the original HW1 structure.</h2>
    <p>If someone wanted to respond to the operating systems topic or comment on the revised Express version of the site, this page provides a place to begin.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-flow">
    <h3>Study contact details</h3>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= study.contactEmail %></p>
    <p><strong>Focus area:</strong> <%= study.assistant.focus %></p>
    <p><strong>Suggested study time:</strong> <%= study.studyTimes[0] %></p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-flow statement-band">
    <p class="eyebrow">Feedback</p>
    <p>Please use this site to review both the operating systems content and the Express implementation. The API used is Open-Meteo and the package used is <code>@faker-js/faker</code>.</p>
  </section>
</main>

